样也在拍拍拍，哈哈😀），然后可能是我从学校后门进去的，找半天没找到考场，真服了我，后面找到啦，然后就进去考试啦，考试的座位挨着好近，我都能看到前面人的题和选项。我旁边那个同学一直看我的，可能他不知道我是菜鸡哈哈😂，最后考出来，就拍个日落吧。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202311052352624.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n","site":{"data":{"about":{"authorinfo":{"leftTags":["🤖️ 数码科技爱好者","🔍 分享与热心帮助","🏠 智能家居小能手","🔨 设计开发一条龙"],"rightTags":["专修交互与设计 🤝","脚踏实地行动派 🏃","团队小组发动机 🧱","壮汉人狠话不多 💢"],"image":"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307060036148.png"},"contentinfo":{"name":"哇子","title":"后端开发者、前端爱好者、博主","product":"优秀的产品","design":"出色的设计","program":"高效的编程","user_experience":"人性化的体验"},"skills":{"title":"技能","subtitle":"开启创造力","tags":[{"title":"Java","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012251124.png","color":"#2f7aff"},{"title":"Linux","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202306192300927.png","color":"#ffffff"},{"title":"Docker","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307021822799.png","color":"#57b6e6"},{"title":"Python","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307021307942.png","color":"#2f7aff"},{"title":"CSS3","color":"#2c51db","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012332911.png"},{"title":"JS","color":"#f7cb4f","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012313073.png"},{"title":"HTML","color":"#e9572b","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012323537.png"},{"title":"Git","color":"#df5b40","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307021314239.png"}]},"careers":{"title":"生涯","subtitle":"无限进步","items":[{"school":"成都信息工程大学","major":"软件工程专业","color":"#357ef5"},{"school":"成都","major":"后端工程师","color":"#eb372a"}],"image":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202306241732028.gif"},"personalities":{"tips":"性格","title":"提倡者","color":"#56a178","type":"INFJ","image":"","link":"https://www.16personalities.com/","linkText":"16personalities","typeLink":"https://www.16personalities.com/ch/infp-%E4%BA%BA%E6%A0%BC","typeName":"提倡者","myphoto":"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307172348269.png"},"motto":{"title":"摘抄","prefix":"活在当下，","content":"去感受生活的热烈和自由。"},"expertise":{"title