s\">https://github.com/boennemann/badges</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>我一般用第一个网站，也就是<a href=\"https://shields.io/%EF%BC%8C%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E3%80%81%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%BE%BD%E7%AB%A0%E3%80%82\">https://shields.io/，支持静态、动态徽章。</a></p>\n<p>打开网站后，点击<strong>get start</strong> 开始制作属于自己的徽章。我一般直接选择<strong>Static Badge</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202311102155903.png\" alt=\"image-20231110215511755\"></p>\n<p>示例：填入以下参数点击生成按钮得到如下徽章</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Static Badge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/v1.0.0-white?label=%E5%93%87%E5%AD%90&labelColor=%2325c2a0&color=white\"></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202311102159100.png\" alt=\"image-20231110215900970\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3、引入\">3、引入</h2>\n<p>生成之后网站提供了很多方式，有URL，MD，HTML，具体就看你自己如何使用了，我一般会在markdown中，嵌入HTML，因为markdown是兼容Html的，一个div class=center 包裹住Github徽章。如果对你有帮助的话，欢迎评论交流。</p>\n","site":{"data":{"about":{"authorinfo":{"leftTags":["🤖️ 数码科技爱好者","🔍 分享与热心帮助","🏠 智能家居小能手","🔨 设计开发一条龙"],"rightTags":["专修交互与设计 🤝","脚踏实地行动派 🏃","团队小组发动机 🧱","壮汉人狠话不多 💢"],"image":"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307060036148.png"},"contentinfo":{"name":"哇子","title":"后端开发者、前端爱好者、博主","product":"优秀的产品","design":"出色的设计","program":"高效的编程","user_experience":"人性化的体验"},"skills":{"title":"技能","subtitle":"开启创造力","tags":[{"title":"Java","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012251124.png","color":"#2f7aff"},{"title":"Linux","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202306192300927.png","color":"#ffffff"},{"title":"Docker","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307021822799.png","color":"#57b6e6"},{"title":"Python","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307021307942.png","color":"#2f7aff"},{"title":"CSS3","color":"#2c51db","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012332911.png"},{"title":"JS","color":"#f7cb4f","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012313073.png"},{"title":"HTML","color":"#e9572b","icon":"http://image.wazicode.top/blog/202307012323537.png"},{"title":"Git