48276-1-1.html</a></p>\n<p>Vscode下载插件：Autojs-VSCodeExt-Fixed</p>\n<p>autojs文档：<a href=\"https://qdgithub.com/docs/autojs/index.html\">https://qdgithub.com/docs/autojs/index.html</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.wazicode.top/blog/202408142327799.png\" alt=\"image-20240814232752616\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"开源项目\">开源项目</h2>\n<p>推荐：<a href=\"https://github.com/wiatingpub/autojs/\">https://github.com/wiatingpub/autojs/</a>              autojs学习项目</p>\n<p>相关介绍：<a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/chen-xia/p/13079588.html\">https://www.cnblogs.com/chen-xia/p/13079588.html</a></p>\n","locate":"成都","cc":"原创","toc":true,"comment":true}],"PostAsset":[],"PostCategory":[{"post_id":"clttzs9sd00096ouhcezlgm9e","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9sl000k6ouhev351pbs"},{"post_id":"clttzs9ry00016ouh573p2gur","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9so000q6ouhd00zbt9p"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sf000b6ouhbzt1ehzj","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9sq000u6ouh8l2qadfl"},{"post_id":"clttzs9si000g6ouhcvv091pg","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9ss000z6ouhh33pbg90"},{"post_id":"clttzs9s500036ouh5uu5ehf5","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9st00126ouhg9lgg9bn"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sb00076ouh9d8thon9","category_id":"clttzs9s800046ouh8n8ca8s0","_id":"clttzs9su00166ouh59do9sj4"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sk000j6ouhg7qkctol","category_id":"clttzs9sq000v6ouhgmbf3ebx","_id":"clttzs9sv00196ouhgoxtfq8u"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sn000p6ouhahkjau9a","category_id":"clttzs9st00136ouhbz9b0shn","_id":"clttzs9sx001e6ouh5xred6qs"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sv001c6ouhh84v18la","category_id":"clttzs9sv001a6ouh038ogkx3","_id":"clttzs9sz001j6ouhcln18ix6"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sp000t6ouhcs2m1apt","category_id":"clttzs9sv001a6ouh038ogkx3","_id":"clttzs9t0001m6ouh1z752470"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sw001d6ouhhooq15ct","category_id":"clttzs9sv001a6ouh038ogkx3","_id":"clttzs9t1001p6ouhcvo35dty"},{"post_id":"clttzs9sx001h6ouhbzvi63k9","category_id":"clttzs9sv00